WEBVTT

00:00:56.507 --> 00:00:58.946
TODAY IS MARCH TWENTY-SEVENTH, NINETEEN NINETY

00:00:58.946 --> 00:01:03.770
FIVE, AND I HAVE THE HONOR OF INTERVIEWING OLGA BITTERMAN IN LOS ANGELES.

00:01:03.770 --> 00:01:05.841
MRS. BITTERMAN

00:01:05.841 --> 00:01:09.631
zogn undz bite ire nomen fun der heym.

00:01:09.631 --> 00:01:11.438
TOBI Vays.

00:01:11.438 --> 00:01:13.262
un ven bistu geboyrn?

00:01:13.262 --> 00:01:15.701
oygust eyn un tsvontsik,

00:01:15.701 --> 00:01:18.683
toyznt nayn hundert dray un tsvontsik.

00:01:18.939 --> 00:01:20.173
un vu bistu geboyrn?

00:01:19.824 --> 00:01:21.175
in Svalyave.

00:01:21.175 --> 00:01:21.936
Svalyave?

00:01:21.473 --> 00:01:22.964
SVALYAVA.

00:01:23.104 --> 00:01:24.098
in CZECHOSLOVAKIA.

00:01:23.631 --> 00:01:27.455
CZECHOSLOVAKIA. demolts iz es geven CZECHOSLOVAKIA.

00:01:27.455 --> 00:01:30.086
vi hobn geheysn dayne eltern?

00:01:30.086 --> 00:01:33.332
mayn tate, olevasholem, hot geheysn

00:01:33.332 --> 00:01:35.350
Mordkhe Itsik Vays,

00:01:35.350 --> 00:01:37.613
un di mame hot geheysn

00:01:37.613 --> 00:01:41.929
Pesl Meyer; m'hot zi gerufn PIR- PIRASKA Meyer.

00:01:41.929 --> 00:01:45.315
un di nomen fun dayne brider un shvestern?

00:01:45.315 --> 00:01:47.578
mayne shvester

00:01:47.578 --> 00:01:50.087
hot geheysn Mal- Malki.

00:01:50.087 --> 00:01:52.280
di tsveyte hot geheysn Ester.

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:55.069
mir hobn zi gerufn ETYU, un

00:01:55.069 --> 00:01:59.122
Mendi iz geven eyn eyntsiker bruder.

00:01:59.122 --> 00:02:01.052
elter, yinger far di?

00:02:01.052 --> 00:02:04.279
der klenster. der yingster vos er iz

00:02:04.279 --> 00:02:07.121
bar-mitsve gevorn in der heym

00:02:07.121 --> 00:02:10.525
befor m'hot undz genumen in

00:02:10.525 --> 00:02:13.156
in geto arayn, oyf Munkatsh.

00:02:13.156 --> 00:02:15.016
un,

00:02:15.016 --> 00:02:19.838
vos hot dayn foter gemakht far a lebn, vos, f- oyf vos hot er gearbet?

00:02:17.472 --> 00:02:18.525
mayn,

00:02:18.525 --> 00:02:23.596
undz ho'mir gehat a tekstil un KONFEKTION gesheft in Svalyave.

00:02:23.596 --> 00:02:26.315
un du kumst fun a frume familye?

00:02:26.315 --> 00:02:27.754
YES.

00:02:27.754 --> 00:02:30.069
mayn tate iz gevezn

00:02:30.069 --> 00:02:33.333
a MO- MODERN talmed-khokhem

00:02:33.333 --> 00:02:35.701
vos yeder hot zikh gerekhnt mit im.

00:02:35.701 --> 00:02:37.999
der rov in Svalyave

00:02:37.999 --> 00:02:40.999
hot nisht gemakht gornisht on mayn tatn.

00:02:40.999 --> 00:02:42.947
mayn tatn iz zeyer a sakh

00:02:42.947 --> 00:02:46.613
tsayt hot er geSPENT mitn rov TOGETHER.

00:02:46.613 --> 00:02:50.403
er iz gevezn zeyer an inteligenter

00:02:50.403 --> 00:02:54.438
mentsh BESIDE a talmed-khokhem.

00:02:54.438 --> 00:02:59.262
vos far a lebn hostu gegat in der heym als kleyn kind?

00:03:01.069 --> 00:03:04.736
di shenste vos se ken zayn.

00:03:04.736 --> 00:03:06.824
di yontoyvim,

00:03:06.824 --> 00:03:10.683
di babe, di zeyde, ales hot gevoynt in Svalyave.

00:03:10.683 --> 00:03:13.385
oder der tate.

00:03:13.385 --> 00:03:16.087
hot khasene gehat fun KOSICE.

00:03:16.087 --> 00:03:18.578
ikh kum, ikh shtam fun KOSICE.

00:03:18.578 --> 00:03:20.946
er hot khasene gehat oyf Svalyave.

00:03:20.946 --> 00:03:23.227
azoy vos ikh fleg

00:03:23.227 --> 00:03:25.315
ven di SCHOOL hot zikh geendikt,

00:03:25.315 --> 00:03:28.683
bin ikh yedns yor geven in KOSICE

00:03:28.683 --> 00:03:31.630
bay di kashoyer FAMILY.

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:35.227
der zeyde, undz ze'mir geven azoy

00:03:35.227 --> 00:03:36.806
CLOSE TOGETHER,

00:03:36.806 --> 00:03:41.631
vos ven ikh fleg ontsukumen mitn tsug als kind aleyn

00:03:41.631 --> 00:03:44.894
ikh gedenk; kh'hob gehat a vays hitl

00:03:44.894 --> 00:03:47.964
un dos hot men shoyn, dos hob ikh aroysgekukt funem tsug,

00:03:47.964 --> 00:03:52.350
un dort iz geshtanen der zeyde mit ale mumes, mit mayn ale COUSINS.

00:03:52.350 --> 00:03:54.754
un gevart ven ikh kum on.

00:03:54.754 --> 00:03:58.350
der zeyde flegt mikh dem tsveytn tog tsu nemen in KOSICE

00:03:58.350 --> 00:04:00.087
un aynkoyfn

00:04:00.087 --> 00:04:06.175
oyskleydn, vayl in Svalyave iz nisht gevezn azelkhe zakhn vos in Kashoy.

00:04:06.175 --> 00:04:09.438
flegt ikh mir, flegt er mikh oystsukleydn.

00:04:09.438 --> 00:04:15.543
oder dos vayse hitl vos di mame hot ongetun mit dem bin ikh yedes yor gekumen biz ikh bin nisht gevezn

00:04:15.543 --> 00:04:22.841
fuftsn yor, SO, di, di FAMILY in Kashoy

00:04:22.841 --> 00:04:24.999
iz gevezn azoy CLOSE

00:04:24.999 --> 00:04:29.665
vayl mayn tate olevasholem iz geven tsvishn finef shvester

00:04:29.665 --> 00:04:32.314
eyn eyntsiker zun.

00:04:32.314 --> 00:04:42.297
un zey hobn mamesh ADMIRED, AND, AND gehaltn farn got dem zun.

00:04:42.297 --> 00:04:46.192
in der heym, undz ho'mir nisht gegesn tsum bayshpil, ikh veys nisht

00:04:46.192 --> 00:04:49.929
tsi du veyst vos dos heyst shtop shmalts un fiter shmalts.

00:04:49.929 --> 00:04:52.069
undz ze'mir geven zeyer frum.

00:04:52.069 --> 00:04:57.140
hobn zey gesh- ge- tsamgeleygt hinern shmalts

00:04:57.140 --> 00:05:00.280
az fun Kashoy hobn mir undz aheymgenumen

00:05:00.280 --> 00:05:04.701
oyf Svalyave, az der tate zol esn dos vos er vil.

00:05:04.701 --> 00:05:08.052
di, di shvesters un di zeyde

00:05:08.052 --> 00:05:13.052
iz gevezn, zey hobn gelib- zey hobn gelebt far dem bruder.

00:05:13.052 --> 00:05:14.736
un far dem eyn eyntsikn zun.

00:05:14.736 --> 00:05:17.999
azoy vi az undz fir kinder funem tatn's

00:05:17.999 --> 00:05:21.701
ze'mir geven di shpiglekh me- MOSTLY

00:05:21.701 --> 00:05:24.649
farn zeydn, vayl dos ze'mir geven dem tatn's kinder.

00:05:24.649 --> 00:05:26.947
YOU KNOW, dem eyn eyntsikn zun's kinder.

00:05:26.947 --> 00:05:28.929
nisht far dem vayl m'hot nisht lib gehat di

00:05:28.929 --> 00:05:31.649
di andere kinder, oder dos iz geven der eyn eyntsiker

00:05:31.649 --> 00:05:34.473
kadish, un er iz geven a gelungener yungerman,

00:05:34.473 --> 00:05:37.911
un, dos, dos iz geven mayn kindheyt.

00:05:37.911 --> 00:05:39.999
ven ikh bin

00:05:39.999 --> 00:05:44.981
in Svalyave, di mame hot oykh gehat zeyer a raykhe FAMILY

00:05:44.981 --> 00:05:46.437
di Meyers,

00:05:46.437 --> 00:05:53.069
vos me ken zey, me ken zey fun nokh haynt oykhet, un me veyst fun zey. ale hobn zey gehat tekstil gesheftn.

00:05:53.069 --> 00:05:57.946
un m'iz geven a CLOSE FAMILY. zeyer a CLOSE FAMILY.

00:05:57.946 --> 00:06:03.174
di, vi ikh bin alt gevezn fuftsn zekhtsn yor,

00:06:03.174 --> 00:06:05.911
kh'hob, shtendik bin ikh geven in gesheft.

00:06:05.911 --> 00:06:07.771
kh'hob tsugeholfn.

00:06:07.771 --> 00:06:10.104
di shvester iz gevezn a,

00:06:10.104 --> 00:06:16.157
in der heym zitsn. zi hot lib gehat tsu kokhn un tsu makhn, un tsu, in der heym.

00:06:16.157 --> 00:06:18.543
ikh bin shtendik gevezn in gesheft.

00:06:18.543 --> 00:06:21.911
SO ven s'iz gekumen di ungerishe tsores tsaytn,

00:06:21.911 --> 00:06:25.648
un mayn tate olevasholem hot gehat a bord,

00:06:25.648 --> 00:06:29.209
un er hot shoyn nisht gekent azoy arumforn,

00:06:29.209 --> 00:06:33.438
hot er mikh geshikt mitn gelt oyf Budapest ayntsukoyfn,

00:06:33.438 --> 00:06:38.087
un, un, ikh hob gebrengt,

00:06:38.087 --> 00:06:41.052
ikh hob gebrengt di skhoyre aheym.

00:06:41.052 --> 00:06:44.069
a sakh mol hob ikh geshikt di skhoyre oyf Munkatsh,

00:06:44.069 --> 00:06:46.350
vos m'hot nisht gekent aheymtsushikn,

00:06:46.350 --> 00:06:49.490
un fun Munkatsh hobn mir es oyfgearbet

00:06:49.490 --> 00:06:53.070
un aheymgebrengt di KONFEKTION skhoyre

00:06:53.070 --> 00:06:55.140
in gesheft arayn.

00:06:55.140 --> 00:07:01.456
un ikh bin gevezn a yung kind, blond.

00:07:01.456 --> 00:07:03.912
m'hot nisht ongezen az ikh bin yidish.

00:07:03.912 --> 00:07:05.877
kh'hob gekent arumforn.

00:07:05.877 --> 00:07:08.332
m'hot mikh nisht legitimirt.

00:07:08.332 --> 00:07:10.999
un eyn STORY hob ikh gehat,

00:07:10.999 --> 00:07:18.666
ikh bin yede vokh aroysgeforn oyf Budapest mitn gelt un brengen di s- di skhoyres aheym.

00:07:18.666 --> 00:07:21.666
eyn mol ven ikh bin geforn

00:07:21.666 --> 00:07:25.420
zenen daytshe ofitsirn aheymgekumen fun di Ukraine.

00:07:25.420 --> 00:07:27.561
du gedenkst velkhe yor dos iz gevezn?

00:07:27.561 --> 00:07:32.403
yo, dos iz gevezn BEGINNING in fir un fertsik.

00:07:32.403 --> 00:07:37.368
un ikh, er hot zikh get- ikh hob mikh nisht get- ikh hob mikh getrofn

00:07:37.368 --> 00:07:40.736
zitsn NEAR dem ofitsir.

00:07:40.736 --> 00:07:43.472
un er heybt tsu mir on tsu redn,

00:07:43.472 --> 00:07:46.911
un dos daytsh hob ikh nisht gut farshtanen.

00:07:46.911 --> 00:07:51.279
ikh hob geredt ungerish, nisht kh'hob, nisht kh'hob farshtanen, oder kh'hob nisht geredt

00:07:51.279 --> 00:07:54.086
HOCHDEUTSCH, SO

00:07:54.086 --> 00:08:00.929
hot er mikh gefregt fun vanet farshteyt. hob ikh gezogt ikh hob gehat a yidishn gelibtn

00:08:00.929 --> 00:08:04.087
un fun dem hob ikh mikh oysgelernt yidish.

00:08:04.087 --> 00:08:06.718
far dem farshtey ikh dos daytshe.

00:08:06.718 --> 00:08:08.929
hot er mir ongehoybn tsu dertseyln

00:08:08.929 --> 00:08:12.841
vi azoy me harget di yidn in Ukraine.

00:08:12.841 --> 00:08:15.753
hot er gezogt "az du bist nisht keyn yidishe

00:08:15.753 --> 00:08:17.613
SO vil ikh dir zogn,

00:08:17.613 --> 00:08:19.438
undz broykhn mir zey nisht,

00:08:19.438 --> 00:08:24.613
undz hobn mir zey gevorfn in vaser arayn, undz viln mir zey in gantsn oysrotn."

00:08:24.613 --> 00:08:26.648
ikh hob dos ales oysgehert,

00:08:26.648 --> 00:08:30.420
biz ze'mir gekumen a sho for Budapest.

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:33.596
dos iz geven a nakht rayze.

00:08:33.596 --> 00:08:38.596
vayl a gantse nakht iz men geforn fun Svalyave fun Munkatsh, oyf Budapest.

00:08:38.596 --> 00:08:41.911
biz m'iz gekumen a sho for Budapest.

00:08:41.911 --> 00:08:43.999
un ven ikh hob mikh derzen

00:08:43.999 --> 00:08:47.543
vayl fa- me fleg mir zikh in di ban trefn

00:08:47.543 --> 00:08:50.420
mit yinglekh un meydlekh un mener un froyen,

00:08:50.420 --> 00:08:54.069
vos zey flegn oykh tsu forn yede vokh oyf Budapest aynkoyfn,

00:08:54.069 --> 00:08:55.735
oder brengen epes a-

00:08:55.735 --> 00:08:57.893
hob ikh mikh ge- moyre gehat

00:08:57.893 --> 00:09:00.981
az er vet, az zey veln tsu mir redn,

00:09:00.981 --> 00:09:04.630
un zey veln oyfdekn az ikh bin a yidishe,

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:11.507
SO bin ikh aropgeshtign in HATVAN hot es geheysn, dos, di di shtot for Budapest

00:09:11.507 --> 00:09:13.016
un mitn pekl,

00:09:13.016 --> 00:09:16.508
un ikh bin farshvundn gevorn, di tsug iz geforn oyf Budapest

00:09:16.508 --> 00:09:21.754
un ikh hob oysgevart dem tsveytn tog dem tsveytn, tsug,

00:09:21.754 --> 00:09:24.087
un azoy bin ikh gekumen oyf Budapest.

00:09:24.087 --> 00:09:27.561
hob ikh shoyn in fir un fertsike BEGINNING aheymgekumen

00:09:27.561 --> 00:09:30.543
un ikh hob gezogt vos kh'hob gehert.

00:09:30.543 --> 00:09:33.017
m'hot gezogt "dos ken nisht zayn."

00:09:33.017 --> 00:09:36.842
"dos ken nisht zayn." oder vos iz geshen?

00:09:36.842 --> 00:09:40.315
me, vi azoy ikh hob gezogt undz ho'mir gehat a tekstil gesheft

00:09:40.315 --> 00:09:43.947
zenen mir nisht gevezn raykhe mentshn, oder balebatishe,

00:09:43.947 --> 00:09:47.596
parnose gehat, azoy vi in EUROPE, s'iz nisht geven milyonern.

00:09:47.596 --> 00:09:52.456
s'iz geven balebatishe, s'iz geven oreme, un s'iz gevezn ra- a bisl raykhe.

00:09:52.456 --> 00:09:56.368
iz gekumen an man, a zeyer guter bakanter

00:09:56.368 --> 00:09:57.841
a FRIEND,

00:09:57.841 --> 00:10:01.350
OF mayn tatn olevasholem, un er hot gebetn

00:10:01.350 --> 00:10:05.929
az er vet batsoln di SPESEN far im

00:10:05.929 --> 00:10:11.438
vayl er hot bakumen a AFFIDAVIT tsu forn oyf Yisroel.

00:10:11.438 --> 00:10:13.858
oyf PALESTINE.

00:10:13.858 --> 00:10:19.911
un zogt er, vayl dos vayb iz tsurikgekumen. far, vi azoy iz dos vayb tsurikgekumen?

00:10:19.911 --> 00:10:25.648
er iz gevezn in arbayts-lager ven me hot genumen di vayb un kinder oyf ukraine.

00:10:25.648 --> 00:10:31.227
demolts hot men undz oykh gebroykht tsu nemen in dem transport.

00:10:31.227 --> 00:10:36.946
nor mayn mame olehasholem iz geven zeyer balibt tsvishn di goyim

00:10:36.946 --> 00:10:40.560
un in STORE, m'hot zi gekent.

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:43.718
iz gekumen a shabes,

00:10:43.718 --> 00:10:45.841
ikh bin ge- aroysgegangen,

00:10:45.841 --> 00:10:50.157
un a man iz mir nokhgegangen, un nokhgegangen un nokhgegangen.

00:10:50.157 --> 00:10:52.631
ikh hob moyre gehat vos der man vil.

00:10:52.631 --> 00:10:54.718
ikh bin gevezn a meydl.

00:10:54.718 --> 00:10:57.525
tref ikh mikh, nokh dem vi ikh kum

00:10:57.525 --> 00:10:59.209
tsu undzer hoyz,

00:10:59.209 --> 00:11:01.999
zogt er mir "vart, meydele" oyf ungerish.

00:11:01.999 --> 00:11:03.244
"vart, meydele."

00:11:03.244 --> 00:11:05.279
"vos, vos vilstu fun mir?"

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:06.402
"horkh her.

00:11:06.402 --> 00:11:09.455
ikh ken dikh, un ikh ken dayn mamen.

00:11:09.455 --> 00:11:12.946
un di m- di shriftn zenen bay mir.

00:11:12.946 --> 00:11:16.104
ikh broykh UNK nokh eyn broykh men avektsushikn,

00:11:16.104 --> 00:11:18.174
vayl dayn tate iz a Kashoyer,

00:11:18.174 --> 00:11:19.753
un er iz nisht,

00:11:19.753 --> 00:11:22.262
er iz" d- dos iz gevorn Ukraine,

00:11:22.262 --> 00:11:24.350
un Kashoy iz gevezn Ungern,

00:11:24.350 --> 00:11:28.104
"vil men enk oyf Ukraine avekshikn.

00:11:28.104 --> 00:11:30.543
ikh vil, zog far di mamen

00:11:30.543 --> 00:11:33.174
ikh bahalt di, di papirn,

00:11:33.174 --> 00:11:38.086
un, un zol men enk nisht avekshikn."

00:11:38.086 --> 00:11:45.472
SO di di mame, az ikh bin aheymgekumen, ikh hob ongetrogn bald matones,

00:11:45.472 --> 00:11:49.472
oyf a kleyd un TEXTILE un THIS, un un gelt.

00:11:49.472 --> 00:11:51.842
un er hot di papirn ge- avekgeleygt.

00:11:51.842 --> 00:11:56.000
oder di froy hot men genumen demolts dem transport.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:59.157
un azoy vi m'hot zi genumen oyf Ukraine,

00:11:59.157 --> 00:12:01.947
un m'hot gebroykht aleyn ven me hot zi genumen

00:12:01.947 --> 00:12:06.456
forn di Dnyeper, der vaser, hot zi dertseylt ven zi iz tsurikgekumen

00:12:06.456 --> 00:12:10.807
hot z- hobn zey gebroykht makhn di griber, un dort hot men zey oysgeshosn.

00:12:10.807 --> 00:12:14.034
zi iz gegangen mit dray kinder.

00:12:14.034 --> 00:12:19.578
hot zi, ven me hot dos ershte kind geshosn, hot zi ongekhapt di tsvey kinder un a-

00:12:19.578 --> 00:12:21.894
arayngefaln in grub arayn.

00:12:21.894 --> 00:12:24.526
oyfn toytn kind un oyf toyte UNK.

00:12:24.526 --> 00:12:28.526
un di iberike toyte zenen oyf ir aroyfgefaln, un zey zenen lebedik geblib- geb-

00:12:28.526 --> 00:12:32.333
UNK, zi hot gehaltn di kinder in, in

00:12:32.333 --> 00:12:33.508
in, in grub.

00:12:33.508 --> 00:12:36.105
ven di daytsh oyf der nakht zenen zey avekgegangen,

00:12:36.105 --> 00:12:39.140
hot zi aroysgekumen fun di, fun dem grub.

00:12:39.140 --> 00:12:42.034
zi hot geheysn MRS SZABO.

00:12:42.034 --> 00:12:45.105
AND mit di tsvey kinder,

00:12:45.105 --> 00:12:47.543
un ongehoybn tsuriktsukumen

00:12:47.543 --> 00:12:50.333
durkh di Karpatn, durkh di grenets.

00:12:50.333 --> 00:12:53.034
iz zi shoyn gekumen mit tsvey, ikh

00:12:53.034 --> 00:12:56.192
az gut gedenk ikh, mit tsvey kinder veyniker,

00:12:56.192 --> 00:12:59.052
oder zi iz tsurikgekumen,

00:12:59.052 --> 00:13:03.648
un far dem iz gekumen MISTER SZABO zogn far mayn tatn olevasholem.

00:13:03.648 --> 00:13:06.911
ikh hob bakumen oyf fir kinder dos,

00:13:06.911 --> 00:13:11.982
di AFFIDAVIT, ikh ken mitnemen oyf PALESTINE tsvey dayne meydlekh.

00:13:11.982 --> 00:13:17.104
loz mir di meydlekh un lomir forn.

00:13:17.104 --> 00:13:18.876
der tate iz geven a frumer.

00:13:18.876 --> 00:13:23.157
meydlekh lozt men nisht oyf PALES- PALESTINE.

00:13:23.157 --> 00:13:26.595
khotshe mayn COUSIN iz aroysgegangen,

00:13:26.595 --> 00:13:28.332
er hot shoyn aroysge-,

00:13:28.332 --> 00:13:33.157
-gangen, vayl er hot gebroykht fun militer fun Kashoy avektsugeyn, iz er shoyn geven in PALESTINE.

