00:18:19.508 --> 00:18:23.912
yidn hobn tsurikbakumen di di IPO-, dos hot geheysn der IPOR,

00:18:23.912 --> 00:18:27.999
dos hot geheysn di bavilikung vayter tsu firn dos gesheft.

