ah in di, in di lager, nisht azoy vayt

00:18:43.297 --> 00:18:46.876
vos di yidn nebekh vos me hot avekgenumen di bavilikungen,

00:18:46.876 --> 00:18:49.561
hobn gef- gebrengt di skhoyres tsun undz,

