zikh rirn, mame hot nisht gevust zuntik in der fri vos es tut zikh oyf der anderer

00:20:50.122 --> 00:20:56.402
zayt shtetele. oder kh'veys nisht, ikh bin aroysgegangen

00:20:56.402 --> 00:20:58.894
un ikh bin arayn in a trafik,

00:20:58.894 --> 00:21:02.069
un dort hot men gezogt se tut zikh groyse zakhn

00:21:02.069 --> 00:21:05.105
mit, meyn ikh me kumt tsamnemen di yidn.

00:21:05.105 --> 00:21:07.368
bin ikh aheymgegangen.

00:21:07.368 --> 00:21:10.561
befor dem, beforn aheymgeyn

00:21:10.561 --> 00:21:12.262
beforn peysekh nokh,

00:21:12.262 --> 00:21:15.508
