00:26:18.578 --> 00:26:22.912
m'hot undz geheysn, in droysn iz gevezn shtroy.

00:26:22.912 --> 00:26:29.298
yeder zol zikh nemen a bintl shtroy un trefn a plats,

00:26:29.298 --> 00:26:31.403
oyfn boydem,

00:26:31.403 --> 00:26:35.631
vi azoy, vu, vayl untn hot men gemakht di tsigl,

00:26:35.631 --> 00:26:37.806
oyfn boydem vu tsu shlofn.

00:26:37.806 --> 00:26:40.648
un azoy ze'mir dort,

00:26:40.648 --> 00:26:45.016
yeder hot zikh gemakht demolts plats un dort ze'mir geshlofn.

00:26:45.016 --> 00:26:48.016
dort hot zikh ongehoybn di tsores.

00:26:48.016 --> 00:26:53.701
di yinglekh hot men genumen yedn tog

00:26:53.701 --> 00:26:59.069
oyf ibungen. zey hobn gezogt ibungen far soldatn.

00:26:59.069 --> 00:27:01.455
oder m'hot zey azoy geplogt,

00:27:01.455 --> 00:27:04.087
un azoy fil ibungen, un azoy fil

00:27:04.087 --> 00:27:06.508
ge- az di mames zenen gezitsn

00:27:06.508 --> 00:27:15.368
un hobn ge- tsugekukt un geveynt un gevart yedes mol yedn nokh mitog di kinder aheym.

00:27:15.368 --> 00:27:21.104
di esns hot men nisht hot, hot men gegebn vos m'hot gekent.

00:27:21.104 --> 00:27:23.385
m'hot aroysgefirt di mener.

00:27:23.385 --> 00:27:26.701
m'hot nisht gelozt shlofn. m'hot aroysgefirt di mener.

00:27:26.701 --> 00:27:28.621
un m'hot zey geheysn in di nakht,

00:27:28.621 --> 00:27:30.526
azoy vi di tate olevasholem,

00:27:30.526 --> 00:27:32.315
er iz nisht geven a gezunter.

00:27:32.315 --> 00:27:35.157
un yedn oyf der nakht hot er gebroykht tsu geyn

00:27:35.157 --> 00:27:38.087
oder, oder ibungen tsu makhn,

00:27:38.087 --> 00:27:42.315
oder kern oder roymen. alts hot men gegebn arbet.

00:27:42.315 --> 00:27:50.403
un alts hot men getsitert un gevart aheym, vayl me hot geshlogn mentshn in der tsvishn ver s'vet kumen der UNK.

00:27:50.403 --> 00:27:54.754
eyn mol iz UNK in, in,

00:27:54.754 --> 00:27:58.543
tsigl fabrik arayngekumen PHOTO,

00:27:58.543 --> 00:28:00.806
mentshn mit PHOTOS,

00:28:00.806 --> 00:28:04.017
mit, mit CAMERAS, PHOTO CAMERAS.

00:28:04.017 --> 00:28:09.613
un me zukht far, far a zhurnal PICTURES.

00:28:09.613 --> 00:28:10.578
PICTURES.

00:28:10.578 --> 00:28:11.811
vosere PICTURE?

00:28:10.688 --> 00:28:13.410
vos, vos far, vos far a mentshn, ungarishe?

00:28:12.892 --> 00:28:16.631
ungarishe, ungarishe. ungarishe fashistn

00:28:16.631 --> 00:28:18.771
zenen gekumen. vosere PICTURES?

00:28:18.771 --> 00:28:22.753
s'iz do dort azoyne sheyne meydlekh, azoyne sheyne yinglekh.

00:28:22.753 --> 00:28:26.244
un zey nemen dos nisht. zey geyen arum zukhndik.

00:28:26.244 --> 00:28:27.508
vos iz?

00:28:27.508 --> 00:28:35.297
zey hobn getrofn a, a a nebekh, nisht a normal kind iz dos gevezn.

00:28:35.297 --> 00:28:37.490
mit di hor

00:28:37.490 --> 00:28:42.683
aropgelozt, ikh veys nisht, di tsung tsi fardreyt, tsi der dos, SO

00:28:42.683 --> 00:28:46.420
dem, dem's PICTURES, biz zey hobn arumgezukht

00:28:46.420 --> 00:28:50.332
dos hobn zey getrofn, un dem PICTURE hobn zey genumen

00:28:50.332 --> 00:28:54.069
un dos hobn zey arayngeshtelt "azoy zeen oys di yidn."

00:28:54.069 --> 00:28:59.736
"un azolkhe yidn, undz broykhn mir zey nisht."

00:28:59.736 --> 00:29:08.262
SO dos, dos iz geven azolkhe shtiklekh, azolkhe vos zenen gekumen az di fashistn kukn.

00:29:08.262 --> 00:29:10.718
nokh dem iz gekumen a fashist,

00:29:10.718 --> 00:29:14.332
un heybt on tsu fregn ver vosere

00:29:14.332 --> 00:29:19.210
ayngeshtelte, vi zey hobn gemakht dos lebn, vi zey hobn gemakht...

00:29:19.210 --> 00:29:21.807
eyn mazl, der tate iz tsugekumen

00:29:21.807 --> 00:29:26.368
ven er hot mikh gefregt un hot gezogt "ikh ho- undz ho'mir gehat a shikh gesheft."

00:29:26.368 --> 00:29:30.228
vayl di shikh gesheft iz nisht gevezn azoy gelt tsu makhn

00:29:30.228 --> 00:29:34.719
vi di TEXTILE. TEXTILE hot men oyf shvarts farkoyft, un m'hot shvarts gekoyft, un

00:29:34.719 --> 00:29:37.210
un m'hot, m'hot gemakht parnose.

00:29:37.210 --> 00:29:40.245
oder di vos zey hobn gezogt,

00:29:40.245 --> 00:29:42.543
di vos hobn gezogt, zey hobn

00:29:42.543 --> 00:29:45.526
TEXTILE, un m'hot gevust raykhe mentshn,

00:29:45.526 --> 00:29:48.526
hot men genumen, "vilt ets kumen aheym?

00:29:48.526 --> 00:29:51.491
vilt ets zen nokh vos, efsher broykht ets epes.

00:29:51.491 --> 00:29:54.684
efsher vet ets nemen epes, vayl vos se broykhts do hobn,

00:29:54.684 --> 00:29:57.613
gold oder m- shmuk oder gelt

00:29:57.613 --> 00:30:00.069
vayl ets vets broykhn oyfn veg tsu hobn."

00:30:00.069 --> 00:30:04.596
un azoy oyf a por meydlekh zenen avek mit di fashistn,

00:30:04.596 --> 00:30:10.034
un hobn gevizn vayl zey hobn gebrengt, biz zey zenen gekumen arayn in TEGLAGYAR, in di

00:30:10.034 --> 00:30:13.174
TEGLAGYAR hot dos geheysn, in di tsigl fabrik.

00:30:13.174 --> 00:30:18.332
un azoy di daytshe ho- zenen arayn in hoyz un hobn durkhgezukht ales,

00:30:18.332 --> 00:30:22.771
un, un zey hobn tsugenumen vayl di meydlekh hobn gevizn

00:30:22.771 --> 00:30:26.209
az, vu zey voynen un vos zey hobn. SO

00:30:26.209 --> 00:30:32.105
mayn tate hot mikh hot, hot mikh geratevet, ikh bin nisht gegangen

00:30:32.105 --> 00:30:37.644
OKAY, far di meydlekh hot men gornisht gekumen. m'hot zey tsurikgebrengt, nor m'hot ales bemeyle tsugenumen.

00:30:37.644 --> 00:30:41.436
a minut.
